name: E.A.T.Works Membership Token: "Happy Mac Sketch" by John F. Simon Jr.

metadata.name: Happy Mac Sketch by John F. Simon Jr.
metadata.description:
This is a sketch that John F. Simon Jr. made in the process of conceptualizing his Every Icon NFT collection.

It is our first thank you gift, recognizing that you have contributed to our membership by attending Salon 0, or supporting our first collection.
